en: wow, actual improvement. previously, the app requires access to gps at all times. now, it only requires location permission while the app is at the foreground. great! new ui can be a bit jarring for users of the older version, but to me, the app seems more responsive and less stalling than before. access to vaccination records are also simplified. great work!
